4363 case CommandType::CMD_STARTUML:
4364 {
4365 QCString jarPath = Config_getString(PLANTUML_JAR_PATH);
4366 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePlantUMLOpt();
4367 parser()->tokenizer.lex();
4368 QCString fullMatch = parser()->context.token->sectionId;
4369 QCString sectionId = "";
4370 int idx = fullMatch.find('{');
4371 int idxEnd = fullMatch.find("}",idx+1);
4372 StringVector optList;
4373 QCString engine;
4374 if (idx != -1) // options present
4375 {
4376 QCString optStr = fullMatch.mid(idx+1,idxEnd-idx-1).stripWhiteSpace();
4377 optList = split(optStr.str(),",");
4378 for (const auto &opt : optList)
4379 {
4380 if (opt.empty()) continue;
4381 bool found = false;
4382 QCString locOpt(opt);
4383 locOpt = locOpt.stripWhiteSpace().lower();
4384 if (g_plantumlEngine.find(locOpt.str())!=g_plantumlEngine.end())
4385 {
4386 if (!engine.isEmpty())
4387 {
4388 warn(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(), "Multiple definition of engine for '\\startuml'");
4389 }
4390 engine = locOpt;
4391 found = true;
4392 }
4393 if (!found)
4394 {
4395 if (sectionId.isEmpty())
4396 {
4397 sectionId = opt;
4398 }
4399 else
4400 {
4401 warn(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Multiple use of filename for '\\startuml'");
4402 }
4403 }
4404 }
4405 }
4406 else
4407 {
4408 sectionId = parser()->context.token->sectionId;
4409 }
4410 if (engine.isEmpty()) engine = "uml";
4411
4412 if (sectionId.isEmpty())
4413 {
4414 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePlantUMLOpt();
4415 retval = parser()->tokenizer.lex();
4416 assert(retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_OK));
4417
4418 sectionId = parser()->context.token->sectionId;
4419 sectionId = sectionId.stripWhiteSpace();
4420 }
4421
4422 QCString plantFile(sectionId);
4423 children().append<DocVerbatim>(parser(),thisVariant(),
4424 parser()->context.context,
4425 parser()->context.token->verb,
4426 DocVerbatim::PlantUML,
4427 FALSE,plantFile);
4428 DocVerbatim *dv = children().get_last<DocVerbatim>();
4429 dv->setEngine(engine);
4430 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePara();
4431 QCString width,height;
4432 parser()->defaultHandleTitleAndSize(CommandType::CMD_STARTUML,&children().back(),dv->children(),width,height);
4433 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePlantUML();
4434 retval = parser()->tokenizer.lex();
4435 int line = 0;
4436 QCString trimmedVerb = stripLeadingAndTrailingEmptyLines(parser()->context.token->verb,line);
4437 if (engine == "ditaa")
4438 {
4439 dv->setUseBitmap(true);
4440 }
4441 else if (engine == "uml")
4442 {
4443 int i = trimmedVerb.find('\n');
4444 QCString firstLine = i==-1 ? trimmedVerb : trimmedVerb.left(i);
4445 if (firstLine.stripWhiteSpace() == "ditaa") dv->setUseBitmap(true);
4446 }
4447 dv->setText(trimmedVerb);
4448 dv->setWidth(width);
4449 dv->setHeight(height);
4450 dv->setLocation(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr());
4451 if (jarPath.isEmpty())
4452 {
4453 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"ignoring \\startuml command because PLANTUML_JAR_PATH is not set");
4454 children().pop_back();
4455 }
4456 if (retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE,TokenRetval::TK_EOF))
4457 {
4458 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"startuml section ended without end marker");
4459 }
4460 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePara();
4461 }
4462 break;
4463 case CommandType::CMD_ENDPARBLOCK:
4464 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndParBlock();
4465 break;
4466 case CommandType::CMD_ENDICODE:
4467 case CommandType::CMD_ENDCODE:
4468 case CommandType::CMD_ENDHTMLONLY:
4469 case CommandType::CMD_ENDMANONLY:
4470 case CommandType::CMD_ENDRTFONLY:
4471 case CommandType::CMD_ENDLATEXONLY:
4472 case CommandType::CMD_ENDXMLONLY:
4473 case CommandType::CMD_ENDDBONLY:
4474 case CommandType::CMD_ENDLINK:
4475 case CommandType::CMD_ENDVERBATIM:
4476 case CommandType::CMD_ENDIVERBATIM:
4477 case CommandType::CMD_ENDILITERAL:
4478 case CommandType::CMD_ENDDOT:
4479 case CommandType::CMD_ENDMSC:
4480 case CommandType::CMD_ENDUML:
4481 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"unexpected command %s",qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
4482 break;
4483 case CommandType::CMD_PARAM:
4484 retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::Param,FALSE,parser()->context.token->paramDir);
4485 break;
4486 case CommandType::CMD_TPARAM:
4487 retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::TemplateParam,FALSE,parser()->context.token->paramDir);
4488 break;
4489 case CommandType::CMD_RETVAL:
4490 retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::RetVal);
4491 break;
4492 case CommandType::CMD_EXCEPTION:
4493 retval = handleParamSection(cmdName,DocParamSect::Exception);
4494 break;
4495 case CommandType::CMD_XREFITEM:
4496 retval = handleXRefItem();
4497 break;
4498 case CommandType::CMD_LINEBREAK:
4499 {
4500 children().append<DocLineBreak>(parser(),thisVariant());
4501 }
4502 break;
4503 case CommandType::CMD_IANCHOR:
4504 case CommandType::CMD_ANCHOR:
4505 {
4506 parser()->handleAnchor(thisVariant(),children());
4507 }
4508 break;
4509 case CommandType::CMD_IPREFIX:
4510 {
4511 parser()->handlePrefix(thisVariant(),children());
4512 }
4513 break;
4514 case CommandType::CMD_ADDINDEX:
4515 {
4516 children().append<DocIndexEntry>(parser(),thisVariant(),
4517 parser()->context.scope!=Doxygen::globalScope?parser()->context.scope:nullptr,
4518 parser()->context.memberDef);
4519 retval = children().get_last<DocIndexEntry>()->parse();
4520 }
4521 break;
4522 case CommandType::CMD_INTERNAL:
4523 retval = Token::make_RetVal_Internal();
4524 break;
4525 case CommandType::CMD_ENDINTERNAL:
4526 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndInternal();
4527 break;
4528 case CommandType::CMD_PARBLOCK:
4529 {
4530 children().append<DocParBlock>(parser(),thisVariant());
4531 retval = children().get_last<DocParBlock>()->parse();
4532 }
4533 break;
4534 case CommandType::CMD_COPYDOC: // fall through
4535 case CommandType::CMD_COPYBRIEF: // fall through
4536 case CommandType::CMD_COPYDETAILS:
4537 //retval = Token::make_RetVal_CopyDoc();
4538 // these commands should already be resolved by processCopyDoc()
4539 break;
4540 case CommandType::CMD_INCLUDE:
4541 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::Include);
4542 break;
4543 case CommandType::CMD_INCWITHLINES:
4544 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::IncWithLines);
4545 break;
4546 case CommandType::CMD_DONTINCLUDE:
4547 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::DontInclude);
4548 break;
4549 case CommandType::CMD_HTMLINCLUDE:
4550 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::HtmlInclude);
4551 break;
4552 case CommandType::CMD_LATEXINCLUDE:
4553 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::LatexInclude);
4554 break;
4555 case CommandType::CMD_RTFINCLUDE:
4556 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::RtfInclude);
4557 break;
4558 case CommandType::CMD_MANINCLUDE:
4559 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::ManInclude);
4560 break;
4561 case CommandType::CMD_XMLINCLUDE:
4562 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::XmlInclude);
4563 break;
4564 case CommandType::CMD_DOCBOOKINCLUDE:
4565 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::DocbookInclude);
4566 break;
4567 case CommandType::CMD_VERBINCLUDE:
4568 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::VerbInclude);
4569 break;
4570 case CommandType::CMD_SNIPPET:
4571 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::Snippet);
4572 break;
4573 case CommandType::CMD_SNIPWITHLINES:
4574 handleInclude(cmdName,DocInclude::SnippetWithLines);
4575 break;
4576 case CommandType::CMD_SKIP:
4577 handleIncludeOperator(cmdName,DocIncOperator::Skip);
4578 break;
4579 case CommandType::CMD_UNTIL:
4580 handleIncludeOperator(cmdName,DocIncOperator::Until);
4581 break;
4582 case CommandType::CMD_SKIPLINE:
4583 handleIncludeOperator(cmdName,DocIncOperator::SkipLine);
4584 break;
4585 case CommandType::CMD_LINE:
4586 handleIncludeOperator(cmdName,DocIncOperator::Line);
4587 break;
4588 case CommandType::CMD_IMAGE:
4589 parser()->handleImage(thisVariant(),children());
4590 break;
4591 case CommandType::CMD_DOTFILE:
4592 if (!Config_getBool(HAVE_DOT))
4593 {
4594 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
4595 "ignoring \\dotfile command because HAVE_DOT is not set");
4596 }
4597 else
4598 {
4599 handleFile<DocDotFile>(cmdName);
4600 }
4601 break;
4602 case CommandType::CMD_VHDLFLOW:
4603 handleVhdlFlow();
4604 break;
4605 case CommandType::CMD_MSCFILE:
4606 handleFile<DocMscFile>(cmdName);
4607 break;
4608 case CommandType::CMD_DIAFILE:
4609 handleFile<DocDiaFile>(cmdName);
4610 break;
4611 case CommandType::CMD_PLANTUMLFILE:
4612 handleFile<DocPlantUmlFile>(cmdName);
4613 break;
4614 case CommandType::CMD_LINK:
4615 handleLink(cmdName,FALSE);
4616 break;
4617 case CommandType::CMD_JAVALINK:
4618 handleLink(cmdName,TRUE);
4619 break;
4620 case CommandType::CMD_CITE:
4621 handleCite(cmdChar,cmdName);
4622 break;
4623 case CommandType::CMD_EMOJI:
4624 handleEmoji(cmdChar,cmdName);
4625 break;
4626 case CommandType::CMD_DOXYCONFIG:
4627 handleDoxyConfig(cmdChar,cmdName);
4628 break;
4629 case CommandType::CMD_REF: // fall through
4630 case CommandType::CMD_SUBPAGE:
4631 handleRef(cmdChar,cmdName);
4632 break;
4633 case CommandType::CMD_SECREFLIST:
4634 {
4635 children().append<DocSecRefList>(parser(),thisVariant());
4636 children().get_last<DocSecRefList>()->parse();
4637 }
4638 break;
4639 case CommandType::CMD_SECREFITEM:
4640 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"unexpected command '%c%s'",cmdChar,qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
4641 break;
4642 case CommandType::CMD_ENDSECREFLIST:
4643 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"unexpected command '%c%s'",cmdChar,qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
4644 break;
4645 case CommandType::CMD_FORMULA:
4646 {
4647 children().append<DocFormula>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->id);
4648 }
4649 break;
4650 //case CommandType::CMD_LANGSWITCH:
4651 // retval = handleLanguageSwitch();
4652 // break;
4653 case CommandType::CMD_INTERNALREF:
4654 //warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"unexpected command %s",qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
4655 {
4656 parser()->handleInternalRef(thisVariant(),children());
4657 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePara();
4658 }
4659 break;
4660 case CommandType::CMD_INHERITDOC:
4661 handleInheritDoc();
4662 break;
4663 case CommandType::CMD_SHOWDATE:
4664 handleShowDate(cmdChar,cmdName);
4665 break;
4666 case CommandType::CMD_ILINE:
4667 handleILine(cmdChar,cmdName);
4668 break;
4669 case CommandType::CMD_IFILE:
4670 handleIFile(cmdChar,cmdName);
4671 break;
4672 case CommandType::CMD_SETSCOPE:
4673 {
4674 parser()->tokenizer.setStateSetScope();
4675 (void)parser()->tokenizer.lex();
4676 parser()->context.context = parser()->context.token->name;
4677 //printf("Found scope='%s'\n",qPrint(parser()->context.context));
4678 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePara();
4679 }
4680 break;
4681 default:
4682 // we should not get here!
4683 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected command '%s' in paragraph context",qPrint(cmdName));
4684 break;
4685 }
4686 INTERNAL_ASSERT(retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE,TokenRetval::TK_EOF,TokenRetval::RetVal_OK,TokenRetval::RetVal_SimpleSec
4687 TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM,TokenRetval::TK_ENDLIST,TokenRetval::TK_NEWPARA
4688 TokenRetval::RetVal_Section,TokenRetval::RetVal_EndList
4689 TokenRetval::RetVal_Internal,TokenRetval::RetVal_SwitchLang
4690 TokenRetval::RetVal_EndInternal)
4691 );
4692 AUTO_TRACE_EXIT("retval={}",retval.to_string());
4693 return retval;
4694}
4695
4696static bool findAttribute(const HtmlAttribList &tagHtmlAttribs,
4697 const char *attrName,
4698 QCString *result)
4699{
4700
4701 for (const auto &opt : tagHtmlAttribs)
4702 {
4703 if (opt.name==attrName)
4704 {
4705 *result = opt.value;
4706 return TRUE;
4707 }
4708 }
4709 return FALSE;
4710}
4711
4712Token DocPara::handleHtmlStartTag(const QCString &tagName,const HtmlAttribList &tagHtmlAttribs)
4713{
4714 AUTO_TRACE("tagName={} #tagHtmlAttrs={}",tagName,tagHtmlAttribs.size());
4715 Token retval = Token::make_RetVal_OK();
4716 HtmlTagType tagId = Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(tagName);
4717 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag && !(tagId>HtmlTagType::XML_CmdMask) &&
4718 tagId!=HtmlTagType::UNKNOWN && tagId!=HtmlTagType::HTML_IMG && tagId!=HtmlTagType::HTML_BR && tagId!=HtmlTagType::HTML_HR && tagId!=HtmlTagType::HTML_P
4719 && tagId!=HtmlTagType::HTML_DIV && tagId!=HtmlTagType::HTML_SPAN)
4720 {
4721 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"HTML tag ('<%s/>') may not use the 'empty tag' XHTML syntax.",
4722 qPrint(tagName));
4723 }
4724 switch (tagId)
4725 {
4726 case HtmlTagType::HTML_UL:
4727 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4728 {
4729 children().append<DocHtmlList>(parser(),thisVariant(),
4730 tagHtmlAttribs,DocHtmlList::Unordered);
4731 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlList>()->parse();
4732 }
4733 break;
4734 case HtmlTagType::HTML_OL:
4735 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4736 {
4737 children().append<DocHtmlList>(parser(),thisVariant(),
4738 tagHtmlAttribs,DocHtmlList::Ordered);
4739 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlList>()->parse();
4740 }
4741 break;
4742 case HtmlTagType::HTML_LI:
4743 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag) break;
4744 if (!insideUL(thisVariant()) && !insideOL(thisVariant()))
4745 {
4746 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"lonely <li> tag found");
4747 }
4748 else
4749 {
4750 retval = Token::make_RetVal_ListItem();
4751 }
4752 break;
4753 case HtmlTagType::HTML_BOLD:
4754 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Bold,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4755 break;
4756 case HtmlTagType::HTML_S:
4757 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::S,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4758 break;
4759 case HtmlTagType::HTML_STRIKE:
4760 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Strike,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4761 break;
4762 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DEL:
4763 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Del,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4764 break;
4765 case HtmlTagType::HTML_UNDERLINE:
4766 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Underline,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4767 break;
4768 case HtmlTagType::HTML_INS:
4769 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Ins,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4770 break;
4771 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CODE:
4772 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag) break;
4773 if (parser()->context.xmlComment)
4774 // for C# source or inside a <summary> or <remark> section we
4775 // treat <code> as an XML tag (so similar to @code)
4776 {
4777 parser()->tokenizer.setStateXmlCode();
4778 retval = handleStartCode();
4779 }
4780 else // normal HTML markup
4781 {
4782 parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Code,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4783 }
4784 break;
4785 case HtmlTagType::HTML_EMPHASIS:
4786 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Italic,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4787 break;
4788 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DIV:
4789 parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Div,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4790 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Div,tagName);
4791 break;
4792 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SPAN:
4793 parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Span,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4794 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Span,tagName);
4795 break;
4796 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SUB:
4797 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Subscript,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4798 break;
4799 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SUP:
4800 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Superscript,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4801 break;
4802 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CENTER:
4803 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Center,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4804 break;
4805 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SMALL:
4806 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Small,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4807 break;
4808 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CITE:
4809 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Cite,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4810 break;
4811 case HtmlTagType::HTML_PRE:
4812 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag) break;
4813 parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Preformatted,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4814 setInsidePreformatted(TRUE);
4815 parser()->tokenizer.setInsidePre(TRUE);
4816 break;
4817 case HtmlTagType::HTML_P:
4818 retval = Token::make_TK_NEWPARA();
4819 break;
4820 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DL:
4821 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4822 {
4823 children().append<DocHtmlDescList>(parser(),thisVariant(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4824 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlDescList>()->parse();
4825 }
4826 break;
4827 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DT:
4828 if (insideDL(thisVariant()))
4829 {
4830 retval = Token::make_RetVal_DescTitle();
4831 }
4832 else
4833 {
4834 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag <dt> found");
4835 }
4836 break;
4837 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DD:
4838 if (insideDL(thisVariant()))
4839 {
4840 retval = Token::make_RetVal_DescData();
4841 }
4842 else
4843 {
4844 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag <dd> found");
4845 }
4846 break;
4847 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TABLE:
4848 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4849 {
4850 children().append<DocHtmlTable>(parser(),thisVariant(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4851 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlTable>()->parse();
4852 }
4853 break;
4854 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TR:
4855 retval = Token::make_RetVal_TableRow();
4856 break;
4857 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TD:
4858 retval = Token::make_RetVal_TableCell();
4859 break;
4860 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TH:
4861 retval = Token::make_RetVal_TableHCell();
4862 break;
4863 case HtmlTagType::HTML_THEAD:
4864 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TBODY:
4865 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TFOOT:
4866 // for time being ignore </t....> tag
4867 break;
4868 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CAPTION:
4869 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag <caption> found");
4870 break;
4871 case HtmlTagType::HTML_BR:
4872 {
4873 children().append<DocLineBreak>(parser(),thisVariant(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4874 }
4875 break;
4876 case HtmlTagType::HTML_HR:
4877 {
4878 children().append<DocHorRuler>(parser(),thisVariant(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4879 }
4880 break;
4881 case HtmlTagType::HTML_A:
4882 retval = parser()->handleAHref(thisVariant(),children(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4883 break;
4884 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H1:
4885 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,1);
4886 break;
4887 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H2:
4888 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,2);
4889 break;
4890 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H3:
4891 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,3);
4892 break;
4893 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H4:
4894 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,4);
4895 break;
4896 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H5:
4897 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,5);
4898 break;
4899 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H6:
4900 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag) retval=handleHtmlHeader(tagHtmlAttribs,6);
4901 break;
4902 case HtmlTagType::HTML_IMG:
4903 {
4904 parser()->handleImg(thisVariant(),children(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4905 }
4906 break;
4907 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DETAILS:
4908 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4909 {
4910 children().append<DocHtmlDetails>(parser(),thisVariant(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4911 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlDetails>()->parse();
4912 }
4913 break;
4914 case HtmlTagType::HTML_BLOCKQUOTE:
4915 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4916 {
4917 children().append<DocHtmlBlockQuote>(parser(),thisVariant(),tagHtmlAttribs);
4918 retval = children().get_last<DocHtmlBlockQuote>()->parse();
4919 }
4920 break;
4921
4922 case HtmlTagType::XML_SUMMARY:
4923 if (insideDetails(thisVariant()))
4924 {
4925 if (!parser()->context.token->emptyTag)
4926 {
4927 DocNodeVariant *n=parent();
4928 while (n && !std::holds_alternative<DocHtmlDetails>(*n)) n=::parent(n);
4929 DocHtmlDetails *d = std::get_if<DocHtmlDetails>(n);
4930 if (d)
4931 {
4932 if (!d->summary()) // details section does not have a summary yet
4933 {
4934 d->parseSummary(n,parser()->context.token->attribs);
4935 }
4936 else
4937 {
4938 retval = Token::make_TK_NEWPARA();
4939 }
4940 }
4941 }
4942 }
4943 break;
4944 case HtmlTagType::XML_REMARKS:
4945 case HtmlTagType::XML_EXAMPLE:
4946 parser()->context.xmlComment=TRUE;
4947 // fall through
4948 case HtmlTagType::XML_VALUE:
4949 case HtmlTagType::XML_PARA:
4950 if (!children().empty())
4951 {
4952 retval = Token::make_TK_NEWPARA();
4953 }
4954 break;
4955 case HtmlTagType::XML_DESCRIPTION:
4956 if (insideTable(thisVariant()))
4957 {
4958 retval = Token::make_RetVal_TableCell();
4959 }
4960 break;
4961 case HtmlTagType::XML_C:
4962 parser()->handleStyleEnter(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Code,tagName,&parser()->context.token->attribs);
4963 break;
4964 case HtmlTagType::XML_PARAM:
4965 case HtmlTagType::XML_TYPEPARAM:
4966 {
4967 parser()->context.xmlComment=TRUE;
4968 QCString paramName;
4969 if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"name",&paramName))
4970 {
4971 if (paramName.isEmpty())
4972 {
4973 if (Config_getBool(WARN_NO_PARAMDOC))
4974 {
4975 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"empty 'name' attribute for <param%s> tag.",tagId==HtmlTagType::XML_PARAM?"":"type");
4976 }
4977 }
4978 else
4979 {
4980 retval = handleParamSection(paramName,
4981 tagId==HtmlTagType::XML_PARAM ? DocParamSect::Param : DocParamSect::TemplateParam,
4982 TRUE);
4983 }
4984 }
4985 else
4986 {
4987 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing 'name' attribute from <param%s> tag.",tagId==HtmlTagType::XML_PARAM?"":"type");
4988 }
4989 }
4990 break;
4991 case HtmlTagType::XML_PARAMREF:
4992 case HtmlTagType::XML_TYPEPARAMREF:
4993 {
4994 QCString paramName;
4995 if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"name",&paramName))
4996 {
4997 //printf("paramName=%s\n",qPrint(paramName));
4998 children().append<DocStyleChange>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.nodeStack.size(),DocStyleChange::Italic,tagName,TRUE);
4999 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(),paramName);
5000 children().append<DocStyleChange>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.nodeStack.size(),DocStyleChange::Italic,tagName,FALSE);
5001 if (!retval.is(TokenRetval::TK_WORD)) children().append<DocWhiteSpace>(parser(),thisVariant()," ");
5002 }
5003 else
5004 {
5005 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing 'name' attribute from <param%sref> tag.",tagId==HtmlTagType::XML_PARAMREF?"":"type");
5006 }
5007 }
5008 break;
5009 case HtmlTagType::XML_EXCEPTION:
5010 {
5011 parser()->context.xmlComment=TRUE;
5012 QCString exceptName;
5013 if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"cref",&exceptName))
5014 {
5015 unescapeCRef(exceptName);
5016 retval = handleParamSection(exceptName,DocParamSect::Exception,TRUE);
5017 }
5018 else
5019 {
5020 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing 'cref' attribute from <exception> tag.");
5021 }
5022 }
5023 break;
5024 case HtmlTagType::XML_ITEM:
5025 case HtmlTagType::XML_LISTHEADER:
5026 if (insideTable(thisVariant()))
5027 {
5028 retval = Token::make_RetVal_TableRow();
5029 }
5030 else if (insideUL(thisVariant()) || insideOL(thisVariant()))
5031 {
5032 retval = Token::make_RetVal_ListItem();
5033 }
5034 else
5035 {
5036 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"lonely <item> tag found");
5037 }
5038 break;
5039 case HtmlTagType::XML_RETURNS:
5040 parser()->context.xmlComment=TRUE;
5041 retval = handleSimpleSection(DocSimpleSect::Return,TRUE);
5042 parser()->context.hasReturnCommand=TRUE;
5043 break;
5044 case HtmlTagType::XML_TERM:
5045 if (insideTable(thisVariant()))
5046 {
5047 retval = Token::make_RetVal_TableCell();
5048 }
5049 break;
5050 case HtmlTagType::XML_SEE:
5051 // I'm not sure if <see> is the same as <seealso> or if it
5052 // should you link a member without producing a section. The
5053 // C# specification is extremely vague about this (but what else
5054 // can we expect from Microsoft...)
5055 {
5056 QCString cref;
5057 //printf("HtmlTagType::XML_SEE: empty tag=%d\n",parser()->context.token->emptyTag);
5058 if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"cref",&cref))
5059 {
5060 unescapeCRef(cref);
5061 if (parser()->context.token->emptyTag) // <see cref="..."/> style
5062 {
5063 bool inSeeBlock = parser()->context.inSeeBlock;
5064 parser()->context.token->name = cref;
5065 parser()->context.inSeeBlock = TRUE;
5066 parser()->handleLinkedWord(thisVariant(),children(),TRUE);
5067 parser()->context.inSeeBlock = inSeeBlock;
5068 }
5069 else // <see cref="...">...</see> style
5070 {
5071 //DocRef *ref = new DocRef(this,cref);
5072 //children().append(ref);
5073 //ref->parse();
5074 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePara();
5075 children().append<DocLink>(parser(),thisVariant(),cref);
5076 DocLink *lnk = children().get_last<DocLink>();
5077 QCString leftOver = lnk->parse(FALSE,TRUE);
5078 if (!leftOver.isEmpty())
5079 {
5080 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(),leftOver);
5081 }
5082 }
5083 }
5084 else if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"langword",&cref)) // <see langword="..."/> or <see langword="..."></see>
5085 {
5086 bool inSeeBlock = parser()->context.inSeeBlock;
5087 parser()->context.token->name = cref;
5088 parser()->context.inSeeBlock = TRUE;
5089 children().append<DocStyleChange>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.nodeStack.size(),DocStyleChange::Code,tagName,TRUE);
5090 parser()->handleLinkedWord(thisVariant(),children(),TRUE);
5091 children().append<DocStyleChange>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.nodeStack.size(),DocStyleChange::Code,tagName,FALSE);
5092 parser()->context.inSeeBlock = inSeeBlock;
5093 }
5094 else
5095 {
5096 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing 'cref' or 'langword' attribute from <see> tag.");
5097 }
5098 }
5099 break;
5100 case HtmlTagType::XML_SEEALSO:
5101 {
5102 parser()->context.xmlComment=TRUE;
5103 QCString cref;
5104 if (findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"cref",&cref))
5105 {
5106 unescapeCRef(cref);
5107 // Look for an existing "see" section
5108 DocNodeVariant *vss=nullptr;
5109 for (auto &n : children())
5110 {
5111 DocSimpleSect *candidate = std::get_if<DocSimpleSect>(&n);
5112 if (candidate && candidate->type()==DocSimpleSect::See)
5113 {
5114 vss = &n;
5115 }
5116 }
5117
5118 if (!vss) // start new section
5119 {
5120 children().append<DocSimpleSect>(parser(),thisVariant(),DocSimpleSect::See);
5121 vss = &children().back();
5122 }
5123
5124 std::get<DocSimpleSect>(*vss).appendLinkWord(cref);
5125 retval = Token::make_RetVal_OK();
5126 }
5127 else
5128 {
5129 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing 'cref' attribute from <seealso> tag.");
5130 }
5131 }
5132 break;
5133 case HtmlTagType::XML_LIST:
5134 {
5135 QCString type;
5136 findAttribute(tagHtmlAttribs,"type",&type);
5137 DocHtmlList::Type listType = DocHtmlList::Unordered;
5138 HtmlAttribList emptyList;
5139 if (type=="number")
5140 {
5141 listType=DocHtmlList::Ordered;
5142 }
5143 if (type=="table")
5144 {
5145 children().append<DocHtmlTable>(parser(),thisVariant(),emptyList);
5146 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlTable>()->parseXml();
5147 }
5148 else
5149 {
5150 children().append<DocHtmlList>(parser(),thisVariant(),emptyList,listType);
5151 retval=children().get_last<DocHtmlList>()->parseXml();
5152 }
5153 }
5154 break;
5155 case HtmlTagType::XML_INCLUDE:
5156 case HtmlTagType::XML_PERMISSION:
5157 // These tags are defined in .Net but are currently unsupported
5158 parser()->context.xmlComment=TRUE;
5159 break;
5160 case HtmlTagType::UNKNOWN:
5161 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unsupported xml/html tag <%s> found", qPrint(tagName));
5162 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(), "<"+tagName+parser()->context.token->attribsStr+">");
5163 break;
5164 case HtmlTagType::XML_INHERITDOC:
5165 handleInheritDoc();
5166 break;
5167 default:
5168 // we should not get here!
5169 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected start tag %s",qPrint(tagName));
5170 ASSERT(0);
5171 break;
5172 }
5173 AUTO_TRACE_EXIT("retval={}",retval.to_string());
5174 return retval;
5175}
5176
5177Token DocPara::handleHtmlEndTag(const QCString &tagName)
5178{
5179 AUTO_TRACE("tagName={}",tagName);
5180 HtmlTagType tagId = Mappers::htmlTagMapper->map(tagName);
5181 Token retval = Token::make_RetVal_OK();
5182 switch (tagId)
5183 {
5184 case HtmlTagType::HTML_UL:
5185 if (!insideUL(thisVariant()))
5186 {
5187 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"found </ul> tag without matching <ul>");
5188 }
5189 else
5190 {
5191 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndList();
5192 }
5193 break;
5194 case HtmlTagType::HTML_OL:
5195 if (!insideOL(thisVariant()))
5196 {
5197 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"found </ol> tag without matching <ol>");
5198 }
5199 else
5200 {
5201 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndList();
5202 }
5203 break;
5204 case HtmlTagType::HTML_LI:
5205 if (!insideLI(thisVariant()))
5206 {
5207 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"found </li> tag without matching <li>");
5208 }
5209 else
5210 {
5211 // ignore </li> tags
5212 }
5213 break;
5214 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DETAILS:
5215 if (!insideDetails(thisVariant()))
5216 {
5217 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"found </details> tag without matching <details>");
5218 }
5219 else
5220 {
5221 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndHtmlDetails();
5222 }
5223 break;
5224 case HtmlTagType::HTML_BLOCKQUOTE:
5225 if (!insideBlockQuote(thisVariant()))
5226 {
5227 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"found </blockquote> tag without matching <blockquote>");
5228 }
5229 else
5230 {
5231 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndBlockQuote();
5232 }
5233 break;
5234 case HtmlTagType::HTML_BOLD:
5235 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Bold,tagName);
5236 break;
5237 case HtmlTagType::HTML_S:
5238 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::S,"s");
5239 break;
5240 case HtmlTagType::HTML_STRIKE:
5241 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Strike,tagName);
5242 break;
5243 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DEL:
5244 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Del,tagName);
5245 break;
5246 case HtmlTagType::HTML_UNDERLINE:
5247 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Underline,tagName);
5248 break;
5249 case HtmlTagType::HTML_INS:
5250 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Ins,tagName);
5251 break;
5252 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CODE:
5253 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Code,tagName);
5254 break;
5255 case HtmlTagType::HTML_EMPHASIS:
5256 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Italic,tagName);
5257 break;
5258 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DIV:
5259 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Div,tagName);
5260 break;
5261 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SPAN:
5262 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Span,tagName);
5263 break;
5264 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SUB:
5265 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Subscript,tagName);
5266 break;
5267 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SUP:
5268 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Superscript,tagName);
5269 break;
5270 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CENTER:
5271 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Center,tagName);
5272 break;
5273 case HtmlTagType::HTML_SMALL:
5274 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Small,tagName);
5275 break;
5276 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CITE:
5277 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Cite,tagName);
5278 break;
5279 case HtmlTagType::HTML_PRE:
5280 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Preformatted,tagName);
5281 setInsidePreformatted(FALSE);
5282 parser()->tokenizer.setInsidePre(FALSE);
5283 break;
5284 case HtmlTagType::HTML_P:
5285 retval = Token::make_TK_NEWPARA();
5286 break;
5287 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DL:
5288 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndDesc();
5289 break;
5290 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DT:
5291 // ignore </dt> tag
5292 break;
5293 case HtmlTagType::HTML_DD:
5294 // ignore </dd> tag
5295 break;
5296 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TABLE:
5297 retval = Token::make_RetVal_EndTable();
5298 break;
5299 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TR:
5300 // ignore </tr> tag
5301 break;
5302 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TD:
5303 // ignore </td> tag
5304 break;
5305 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TH:
5306 // ignore </th> tag
5307 break;
5308 case HtmlTagType::HTML_THEAD:
5309 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TBODY:
5310 case HtmlTagType::HTML_TFOOT:
5311 // for time being ignore </t....> tag
5312 break;
5313 case HtmlTagType::HTML_CAPTION:
5314 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </caption> found");
5315 break;
5316 case HtmlTagType::HTML_BR:
5317 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Illegal </br> tag found");
5318 break;
5319 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H1:
5320 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </h1> found");
5321 break;
5322 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H2:
5323 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </h2> found");
5324 break;
5325 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H3:
5326 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </h3> found");
5327 break;
5328 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H4:
5329 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </h4> found");
5330 break;
5331 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H5:
5332 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </h5> found");
5333 break;
5334 case HtmlTagType::HTML_H6:
5335 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </h6> found");
5336 break;
5337 case HtmlTagType::HTML_IMG:
5338 break;
5339 case HtmlTagType::HTML_HR:
5340 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Illegal </hr> tag found");
5341 break;
5342 case HtmlTagType::HTML_A:
5343 //warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected tag </a> found");
5344 // ignore </a> tag (can be part of <a name=...></a>
5345 break;
5346
5347 case HtmlTagType::XML_TERM:
5348 break;
5349 case HtmlTagType::XML_SUMMARY:
5350 retval = Token::make_TK_NEWPARA();
5351 break;
5352 case HtmlTagType::XML_REMARKS:
5353 case HtmlTagType::XML_PARA:
5354 case HtmlTagType::XML_VALUE:
5355 case HtmlTagType::XML_EXAMPLE:
5356 case HtmlTagType::XML_PARAM:
5357 case HtmlTagType::XML_LIST:
5358 case HtmlTagType::XML_TYPEPARAM:
5359 case HtmlTagType::XML_RETURNS:
5360 case HtmlTagType::XML_SEE:
5361 case HtmlTagType::XML_SEEALSO:
5362 case HtmlTagType::XML_EXCEPTION:
5363 case HtmlTagType::XML_INHERITDOC:
5364 retval = Token::make_RetVal_CloseXml();
5365 break;
5366 case HtmlTagType::XML_C:
5367 parser()->handleStyleLeave(thisVariant(),children(),DocStyleChange::Code,tagName);
5368 break;
5369 case HtmlTagType::XML_ITEM:
5370 case HtmlTagType::XML_LISTHEADER:
5371 case HtmlTagType::XML_INCLUDE:
5372 case HtmlTagType::XML_PERMISSION:
5373 case HtmlTagType::XML_DESCRIPTION:
5374 case HtmlTagType::XML_PARAMREF:
5375 case HtmlTagType::XML_TYPEPARAMREF:
5376 // These tags are defined in .Net but are currently unsupported
5377 break;
5378 case HtmlTagType::UNKNOWN:
5379 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unsupported xml/html tag </%s> found", qPrint(tagName));
5380 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(),"</"+tagName+">");
5381 break;
5382 default:
5383 // we should not get here!
5384 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected end tag %s",qPrint(tagName));
5385 ASSERT(0);
5386 break;
5387 }
5388 AUTO_TRACE_EXIT("retval={}",retval.to_string());
5389 return retval;
5390}
5391
5392static bool checkIfHtmlEndTagEndsAutoList(DocParser *parser,const DocNodeVariant *n)
5393{
5394 // expected hierarchy:
5395 // 1. DocAutoListItem <- n
5396 // 2. DocAutoList <- parent(n)
5397 // 3. DocPara <- parent(parent(n))
5398
5399 // step 1
5400 if (!std::get_if<DocAutoListItem>(n)) // not inside a auto list item
5401 {
5402 return false;
5403 }
5404
5405 // step 2
5406 n = parent(n);
5407 int indent = 0;
5408 const auto docAutoList = std::get_if<DocAutoList>(n);
5409 if (docAutoList) // capture indent
5410 {
5411 indent = docAutoList->indent();
5412 }
5413 else
5414 {
5415 return false;
5416 }
5417
5418 // step 3
5419 n = parent(n);
5420 const auto docPara = std::get_if<DocPara>(n);
5421 if (docPara)
5422 {
5423 QCString tagNameLower = QCString(parser->context.token->name).lower();
5424 auto topStyleChange = [](const DocStyleChangeStack &stack) -> const DocStyleChange &
5425 {
5426 return std::get<DocStyleChange>(*stack.top());
5427 };
5428
5429 if (parser->context.styleStack.empty() || // no style change
5430 (topStyleChange(parser->context.styleStack).tagName()==tagNameLower && // correct style change
5431 topStyleChange(parser->context.styleStack).position()!=parser->context.nodeStack.size()) // wrong position, so normal close
5432 )
5433 {
5434 // insert an artificial 'end of autolist' marker and parse again
5435 QCString indentStr;
5436 indentStr.fill(' ',indent);
5437 parser->tokenizer.unputString("\\ilinebr "+indentStr+".\\ilinebr"+indentStr+"</"+parser->context.token->name+">");
5438 return true;
5439 }
5440 }
5441 return false;
5442}
5443
5444Token DocPara::parse()
5445{
5446 AUTO_TRACE();
5447 auto ns = AutoNodeStack(parser(),thisVariant());
5448 // handle style commands "inherited" from the previous paragraph
5449 parser()->handleInitialStyleCommands(thisVariant(),children());
5450 Token tok=parser()->tokenizer.lex();
5451 Token retval = Token::make_TK_NONE();
5452 while (!tok.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE, TokenRetval::TK_EOF)) // get the next token
5453 {
5454reparsetoken:
5455 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("token '{}' at {}",tok.to_string(),parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr());
5456 if (tok.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_WORD,TokenRetval::TK_LNKWORD,TokenRetval::TK_SYMBOL,TokenRetval::TK_URL,
5457 TokenRetval::TK_COMMAND_AT,TokenRetval::TK_COMMAND_BS,TokenRetval::TK_HTMLTAG)
5458 )
5459 {
5460 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("name={}",parser()->context.token->name);
5461 }
5462 switch(tok.value())
5463 {
5464 case TokenRetval::TK_WORD:
5465 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->name);
5466 break;
5467 case TokenRetval::TK_LNKWORD:
5468 parser()->handleLinkedWord(thisVariant(),children());
5469 break;
5470 case TokenRetval::TK_URL:
5471 children().append<DocURL>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->name,parser()->context.token->isEMailAddr);
5472 break;
5473 case TokenRetval::TK_WHITESPACE:
5474 {
5475 // prevent leading whitespace and collapse multiple whitespace areas
5476 if (insidePRE(thisVariant()) || // all whitespace is relevant
5477 (
5478 // remove leading whitespace
5479 !children().empty() &&
5480 // and whitespace after certain constructs
5481 !holds_one_of_alternatives<DocHtmlDescList, DocHtmlTable, DocHtmlList, DocSimpleSect,
5482 DocAutoList, DocSimpleList, DocHtmlHeader, DocHtmlBlockQuote,
5483 DocParamSect, DocHtmlDetails, DocXRefItem>(children().back())
5484 )
5485 )
5486 {
5487 children().append<DocWhiteSpace>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->chars);
5488 }
5489 }
5490 break;
5491 case TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM:
5492 {
5493 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("found list item at {}",parser()->context.token->indent);
5494 const DocNodeVariant *n=parent();
5495 while (n && !std::holds_alternative<DocAutoList>(*n)) n=::parent(n);
5496 const DocAutoList *al = std::get_if<DocAutoList>(n);
5497 if (al) // we found an auto list up in the hierarchy
5498 {
5499 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("previous list item at {}",al->indent());
5500 if (al->indent()>=parser()->context.token->indent)
5501 // new item at the same or lower indent level
5502 {
5503 retval = Token::make_TK_LISTITEM();
5504 goto endparagraph;
5505 }
5506 }
5507
5508 // determine list depth
5509 int depth = 0;
5510 n=parent();
5511 while (n)
5512 {
5513 al = std::get_if<DocAutoList>(n);
5514 if (al && al->isEnumList()) depth++;
5515 n=::parent(n);
5516 }
5517
5518 // first item or sub list => create new list
5519 do
5520 {
5521 children().append<DocAutoList>(parser(),thisVariant(),
5522 parser()->context.token->indent,
5523 parser()->context.token->isEnumList,depth,
5524 parser()->context.token->isCheckedList);
5525 al = children().get_last<DocAutoList>();
5526 retval = children().get_last<DocAutoList>()->parse();
5527 } while (retval.is(TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM) && // new list
5528 al->indent()==parser()->context.token->indent // at same indent level
5529 );
5530
5531 // check the return value
5532 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_SimpleSec)) // auto list ended due to simple section command
5533 {
5534 // Reparse the token that ended the section at this level,
5535 // so a new simple section will be started at this level.
5536 // This is the same as unputting the last read token and continuing.
5537 parser()->context.token->name = parser()->context.token->simpleSectName;
5538 if (parser()->context.token->name.startsWith("rcs:")) // RCS section
5539 {
5540 parser()->context.token->name = parser()->context.token->name.mid(4);
5541 parser()->context.token->text = parser()->context.token->simpleSectText;
5542 tok = Token::make_TK_RCSTAG();
5543 }
5544 else // other section
5545 {
5546 tok = Token::make_TK_COMMAND_BS();
5547 }
5548 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("reparsing command {}",parser()->context.token->name);
5549 goto reparsetoken;
5550 }
5551 else if (retval.is(TokenRetval::TK_ENDLIST))
5552 {
5553 if (al->indent()>parser()->context.token->indent) // end list
5554 {
5555 goto endparagraph;
5556 }
5557 else // continue with current paragraph
5558 {
5559 }
5560 }
5561 else // paragraph ended due to TokenRetval::TK_NEWPARA, TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM, or EOF
5562 {
5563 goto endparagraph;
5564 }
5565 }
5566 break;
5567 case TokenRetval::TK_ENDLIST:
5568 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("Found end of list inside of paragraph at line {}",parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr());
5569 if (std::get_if<DocAutoListItem>(parent()))
5570 {
5571 const DocAutoList *al = std::get_if<DocAutoList>(::parent(parent()));
5572 if (al && al->indent()>=parser()->context.token->indent)
5573 {
5574 // end of list marker ends this paragraph
5575 retval = Token::make_TK_ENDLIST();
5576 goto endparagraph;
5577 }
5578 else
5579 {
5580 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"End of list marker found "
5581 "has invalid indent level");
5582 }
5583 }
5584 else
5585 {
5586 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"End of list marker found without any preceding "
5587 "list items");
5588 }
5589 break;
5590 case TokenRetval::TK_COMMAND_AT:
5591 // fall through
5592 case TokenRetval::TK_COMMAND_BS:
5593 {
5594 // see if we have to start a simple section
5595 CommandType cmd = Mappers::cmdMapper->map(parser()->context.token->name);
5596 const DocNodeVariant *n=parent();
5597 while (n && !std::holds_alternative<DocSimpleSect>(*n) &&
5598 !std::holds_alternative<DocParamSect>(*n))
5599 {
5600 n=::parent(n);
5601 }
5602 if (cmd>CommandType::SIMPLESECT_BIT)
5603 {
5604 if (n) // already in a simple section
5605 {
5606 // simple section cannot start in this paragraph, need
5607 // to unwind the stack and remember the command.
5608 parser()->context.token->simpleSectName = parser()->context.token->name;
5609 retval = Token::make_RetVal_SimpleSec();
5610 goto endparagraph;
5611 }
5612 }
5613 // see if we are in a simple list
5614 n=parent();
5615 while (n && !std::holds_alternative<DocSimpleListItem>(*n)) n=::parent(n);
5616 if (n)
5617 {
5618 if (cmd==CommandType::CMD_LI)
5619 {
5620 retval = Token::make_RetVal_ListItem();
5621 goto endparagraph;
5622 }
5623 }
5624
5625 // handle the command
5626 retval=handleCommand(tok.command_to_char(),parser()->context.token->name);
5627 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("handleCommand returns {}",retval.to_string());
5628
5629 // check the return value
5630 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_SimpleSec))
5631 {
5632 // Reparse the token that ended the section at this level,
5633 // so a new simple section will be started at this level.
5634 // This is the same as unputting the last read token and continuing.
5635 parser()->context.token->name = parser()->context.token->simpleSectName;
5636 if (parser()->context.token->name.startsWith("rcs:")) // RCS section
5637 {
5638 parser()->context.token->name = parser()->context.token->name.mid(4);
5639 parser()->context.token->text = parser()->context.token->simpleSectText;
5640 tok = Token::make_TK_RCSTAG();
5641 }
5642 else // other section
5643 {
5644 tok = Token::make_TK_COMMAND_BS();
5645 }
5646 AUTO_TRACE_ADD("reparsing command {}",parser()->context.token->name);
5647 goto reparsetoken;
5648 }
5649 else if (retval.value()>TokenRetval::TK_NONE && retval.value()<TokenRetval::RetVal_OK)
5650 {
5651 // the command ended with a new command, reparse this token
5652 tok = retval;
5653 goto reparsetoken;
5654 }
5655 else if (retval.value()!=TokenRetval::RetVal_OK) // end of file, end of paragraph, start or end of section
5656 // or some auto list marker
5657 {
5658 goto endparagraph;
5659 }
5660 }
5661 break;
5662 case TokenRetval::TK_HTMLTAG:
5663 {
5664 if (!parser()->context.token->endTag) // found a start tag
5665 {
5666 retval = handleHtmlStartTag(parser()->context.token->name,parser()->context.token->attribs);
5667 }
5668 else // found an end tag
5669 {
5670 if (checkIfHtmlEndTagEndsAutoList(parser(),parent()))
5671 {
5672 break; // new code has been pushed back to the scanner, need to reparse
5673 }
5674 retval = handleHtmlEndTag(parser()->context.token->name);
5675 }
5676 if (!retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_OK))
5677 {
5678 goto endparagraph;
5679 }
5680 }
5681 break;
5682 case TokenRetval::TK_SYMBOL:
5683 {
5684 HtmlEntityMapper::SymType s = DocSymbol::decodeSymbol(parser()->context.token->name);
5685 if (s!=HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Unknown)
5686 {
5687 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),s);
5688 }
5689 else
5690 {
5691 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->name);
5692 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unsupported symbol '%s' found",
5693 qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
5694 }
5695 break;
5696 }
5697 case TokenRetval::TK_NEWPARA:
5698 retval = Token::make_TK_NEWPARA();
5699 goto endparagraph;
5700 case TokenRetval::TK_RCSTAG:
5701 {
5702 const DocNodeVariant *n=parent();
5703 while (n && !std::holds_alternative<DocSimpleSect>(*n) &&
5704 !std::holds_alternative<DocParamSect>(*n))
5705 {
5706 n=::parent(n);
5707 }
5708 if (n) // already in a simple section
5709 {
5710 // simple section cannot start in this paragraph, need
5711 // to unwind the stack and remember the command.
5712 parser()->context.token->simpleSectName = "rcs:"+parser()->context.token->name;
5713 parser()->context.token->simpleSectText = parser()->context.token->text;
5714 retval = Token::make_RetVal_SimpleSec();
5715 goto endparagraph;
5716 }
5717
5718 // see if we are in a simple list
5719 children().append<DocSimpleSect>(parser(),thisVariant(),DocSimpleSect::Rcs);
5720 children().get_last<DocSimpleSect>()->parseRcs();
5721 }
5722 break;
5723 default:
5724 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
5725 "Found unexpected token (id=%s)",tok.to_string());
5726 break;
5727 }
5728 tok=parser()->tokenizer.lex();
5729 }
5730 retval=Token::make_TK_NONE();
5731endparagraph:
5732 parser()->handlePendingStyleCommands(thisVariant(),children());
5733 DocPara *par = std::get_if<DocPara>(parser()->context.nodeStack.top());
5734 if (!parser()->context.token->endTag && par &&
5735 retval.is(TokenRetval::TK_NEWPARA) && parser()->context.token->name.lower() == "p")
5736 {
5737 par->setAttribs(parser()->context.token->attribs);
5738 }
5739 INTERNAL_ASSERT(retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE,TokenRetval::TK_EOF,TokenRetval::TK_NEWPARA,TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM,
5740 TokenRetval::TK_ENDLIST,TokenRetval::RetVal_OK)
5741 );
5742
5743 AUTO_TRACE_EXIT("retval={}",retval.to_string());
5744 return retval;
5745}
5746
5747//--------------------------------------------------------------------------
5748
5749Token DocSection::parse()
5750{
5751 AUTO_TRACE("start {} level={}", parser()->context.token->sectionId, m_level);
5752 Token retval = Token::make_RetVal_OK();
5753 auto ns = AutoNodeStack(parser(),thisVariant());
5754
5755 if (!m_id.isEmpty())
5756 {
5757 const SectionInfo *sec = SectionManager::instance().find(m_id);
5758 if (sec)
5759 {
5760 m_file = sec->fileName();
5761 m_anchor = sec->label();
5762 QCString titleStr = sec->title();
5763 if (titleStr.isEmpty()) titleStr = sec->label();
5764 m_title = createDocNode<DocTitle>(parser(),thisVariant());
5765 DocTitle *title = &std::get<DocTitle>(*m_title);
5766 title->parseFromString(thisVariant(),titleStr);
5767 }
5768 }
5769
5770 // first parse any number of paragraphs
5771 bool isFirst=TRUE;
5772 DocPara *lastPar=nullptr;
5773 do
5774 {
5775 children().append<DocPara>(parser(),thisVariant());
5776 DocPara *par = children().get_last<DocPara>();
5777 if (isFirst) { par->markFirst(); isFirst=FALSE; }
5778 retval=par->parse();
5779 if (!par->isEmpty())
5780 {
5781 if (lastPar) lastPar->markLast(FALSE);
5782 lastPar = par;
5783 }
5784 else
5785 {
5786 children().pop_back();
5787 }
5788 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM))
5789 {
5790 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Invalid list item found");
5791 }
5792 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Internal))
5793 {
5794 children().append<DocInternal>(parser(),thisVariant());
5795 retval = children().get_last<DocInternal>()->parse(m_level+1);
5796 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_EndInternal))
5797 {
5798 retval = Token::make_RetVal_OK();
5799 }
5800 }
5801 } while (!retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE, TokenRetval::TK_EOF, TokenRetval::RetVal_Section, TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection,
5802 TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection, TokenRetval::RetVal_Paragraph, TokenRetval::RetVal_SubParagraph,
5803 TokenRetval::RetVal_SubSubParagraph, TokenRetval::RetVal_EndInternal)
5804 );
5805
5806 if (lastPar) lastPar->markLast();
5807
5808 while (true)
5809 {
5810 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection) && m_level<=1)
5811 {
5812 // then parse any number of nested sections
5813 while (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection)) // more sections follow
5814 {
5815 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
5816 2,
5817 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
5818 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
5819 }
5820 break;
5821 }
5822 else if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection) && m_level<=2)
5823 {
5824 if ((m_level <= 1) &&
5825 !AnchorGenerator::instance().isGenerated(parser()->context.token->sectionId.str()))
5826 {
5827 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,
5828 parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
5829 "Unexpected subsubsection command found inside %s!",
5830 g_sectionLevelToName[m_level]);
5831 }
5832 // then parse any number of nested sections
5833 while (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection)) // more sections follow
5834 {
5835 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
5836 3,
5837 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
5838 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
5839 }
5840 if (!(m_level < 2 && retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection))) break;
5841 }
5842 else if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Paragraph) && m_level<=3)
5843 {
5844 if ((m_level <= 2) &&
5845 !AnchorGenerator::instance().isGenerated(parser()->context.token->sectionId.str()))
5846 {
5847 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
5848 "Unexpected paragraph command found inside %s!",
5849 g_sectionLevelToName[m_level]);
5850 }
5851 // then parse any number of nested sections
5852 while (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Paragraph)) // more sections follow
5853 {
5854 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
5855 4,
5856 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
5857 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
5858 }
5859 if (!(m_level<3 && (retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection,TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection)))) break;
5860 }
5861 else if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_SubParagraph) && m_level<=4)
5862 {
5863 if ((m_level <= 3) &&
5864 !AnchorGenerator::instance().isGenerated(parser()->context.token->sectionId.str()))
5865 {
5866 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
5867 "Unexpected subparagraph command found inside %s!",
5868 g_sectionLevelToName[m_level]);
5869 }
5870 // then parse any number of nested sections
5871 while (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_SubParagraph)) // more sections follow
5872 {
5873 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
5874 5,
5875 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
5876 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
5877 }
5878 if (!(m_level<4 && (retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection,TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection,TokenRetval::RetVal_Paragraph)))) break;
5879 }
5880 else if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_SubSubParagraph) && m_level<=5)
5881 {
5882 if ((m_level <= 4) &&
5883 !AnchorGenerator::instance().isGenerated(parser()->context.token->sectionId.str()))
5884 {
5885 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
5886 "Unexpected subsubparagraph command found inside %s!",
5887 g_sectionLevelToName[m_level]);
5888 }
5889 // then parse any number of nested sections
5890 while (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_SubSubParagraph)) // more sections follow
5891 {
5892 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
5893 6,
5894 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
5895 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
5896 }
5897 if (!(m_level<5 && (retval.is_any_of( TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection, TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection,
5898 TokenRetval::RetVal_Paragraph, TokenRetval::RetVal_SubParagraph)))) break;
5899 }
5900 else
5901 {
5902 break;
5903 }
5904 }
5905
5906 INTERNAL_ASSERT(retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE, TokenRetval::TK_EOF,
5907 TokenRetval::RetVal_Section, TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsection,
5908 TokenRetval::RetVal_Subsubsection, TokenRetval::RetVal_Paragraph,
5909 TokenRetval::RetVal_SubParagraph, TokenRetval::RetVal_SubSubParagraph,
5910 TokenRetval::RetVal_Internal, TokenRetval::RetVal_EndInternal)
5911 );
5912
5913 AUTO_TRACE_EXIT("retval={}", retval.to_string());
5914 return retval;
5915}
5916
5917//--------------------------------------------------------------------------
5918
5919void DocText::parse()
5920{
5921 AUTO_TRACE();
5922 auto ns = AutoNodeStack(parser(),thisVariant());
5923 parser()->tokenizer.setStateText();
5924
5925 Token tok = parser()->tokenizer.lex();
5926 while (!tok.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE, TokenRetval::TK_EOF)) // get the next token
5927 {
5928 switch(tok.value())
5929 {
5930 case TokenRetval::TK_WORD:
5931 children().append<DocWord>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->name);
5932 break;
5933 case TokenRetval::TK_WHITESPACE:
5934 children().append<DocWhiteSpace>(parser(),thisVariant(),parser()->context.token->chars);
5935 break;
5936 case TokenRetval::TK_SYMBOL:
5937 {
5938 HtmlEntityMapper::SymType s = DocSymbol::decodeSymbol(parser()->context.token->name);
5939 if (s!=HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Unknown)
5940 {
5941 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),s);
5942 }
5943 else
5944 {
5945 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unsupported symbol '%s' found",
5946 qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
5947 }
5948 }
5949 break;
5950 case TokenRetval::TK_COMMAND_AT:
5951 // fall through
5952 case TokenRetval::TK_COMMAND_BS:
5953 switch (Mappers::cmdMapper->map(parser()->context.token->name))
5954 {
5955 case CommandType::CMD_BSLASH:
5956 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_BSlash);
5957 break;
5958 case CommandType::CMD_AT:
5959 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_At);
5960 break;
5961 case CommandType::CMD_LESS:
5962 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Less);
5963 break;
5964 case CommandType::CMD_GREATER:
5965 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Greater);
5966 break;
5967 case CommandType::CMD_AMP:
5968 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Amp);
5969 break;
5970 case CommandType::CMD_DOLLAR:
5971 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Dollar);
5972 break;
5973 case CommandType::CMD_HASH:
5974 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Hash);
5975 break;
5976 case CommandType::CMD_DCOLON:
5977 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_DoubleColon);
5978 break;
5979 case CommandType::CMD_PERCENT:
5980 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Percent);
5981 break;
5982 case CommandType::CMD_NDASH:
5983 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Minus);
5984 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Minus);
5985 break;
5986 case CommandType::CMD_MDASH:
5987 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Minus);
5988 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Minus);
5989 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Minus);
5990 break;
5991 case CommandType::CMD_QUOTE:
5992 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Quot);
5993 break;
5994 case CommandType::CMD_PUNT:
5995 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Dot);
5996 break;
5997 case CommandType::CMD_PLUS:
5998 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Plus);
5999 break;
6000 case CommandType::CMD_MINUS:
6001 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Minus);
6002 break;
6003 case CommandType::CMD_EQUAL:
6004 children().append<DocSymbol>(parser(),thisVariant(),HtmlEntityMapper::Sym_Equal);
6005 break;
6006 default:
6007 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected command '%s' found",
6008 qPrint(parser()->context.token->name));
6009 break;
6010 }
6011 break;
6012 default:
6013 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Unexpected token %s",
6014 tok.to_string());
6015 break;
6016 }
6017 tok = parser()->tokenizer.lex();
6018 }
6019
6020 parser()->handleUnclosedStyleCommands();
6021
6022}
6023
6024
6025//--------------------------------------------------------------------------
6026
6027void DocRoot::parse()
6028{
6029 AUTO_TRACE();
6030 auto ns = AutoNodeStack(parser(),thisVariant());
6031 parser()->tokenizer.setStatePara();
6032 Token retval = Token::make_TK_NONE();
6033
6034 // first parse any number of paragraphs
6035 bool isFirst=TRUE;
6036 DocPara *lastPar = nullptr;
6037 do
6038 {
6039 {
6040 children().append<DocPara>(parser(),thisVariant());
6041 DocPara *par = children().get_last<DocPara>();
6042 if (isFirst) { par->markFirst(); isFirst=FALSE; }
6043 retval=par->parse();
6044 if (par->isEmpty() && par->attribs().empty())
6045 {
6046 children().pop_back();
6047 }
6048 else
6049 {
6050 lastPar = par;
6051 }
6052 }
6053 auto checkParagraph = [this,&retval](Token t,int level,const char *sectionType,const char *parentSectionType) {
6054 if (retval == t)
6055 {
6056 if (!AnchorGenerator::instance().isGenerated(parser()->context.token->sectionId.str()))
6057 {
6058 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,
6059 parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),
6060 "found %s command (id: '%s') outside of %s context!",
6061 sectionType,qPrint(parser()->context.token->sectionId),parentSectionType);
6062 }
6063 while (retval==t)
6064 {
6065 if (!parser()->context.token->sectionId.isEmpty())
6066 {
6067 const SectionInfo *sec=SectionManager::instance().find(parser()->context.token->sectionId);
6068 if (sec)
6069 {
6070 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
6071 level,
6072 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
6073 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
6074 }
6075 else
6076 {
6077 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Invalid %s id '%s'; ignoring %s",
6078 sectionType,qPrint(parser()->context.token->sectionId),sectionType);
6079 retval = Token::make_TK_NONE();
6080 }
6081 }
6082 else
6083 {
6084 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing id for %s; ignoring %s",sectionType,sectionType);
6085 retval = Token::make_TK_NONE();
6086 }
6087 }
6088 }
6089 };
6090 checkParagraph(Token::make_RetVal_SubSubParagraph(), 6, "subsubparagraph", "subparagraph" );
6091 checkParagraph(Token::make_RetVal_SubParagraph(), 5, "subparagraph", "paragraph" );
6092 checkParagraph(Token::make_RetVal_Paragraph(), 4, "paragraph", "subsubsection" );
6093 checkParagraph(Token::make_RetVal_Subsubsection(), 3, "subsubsection", "subsection" );
6094 checkParagraph(Token::make_RetVal_Subsection(), 2, "subsection", "section" );
6095
6096 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::TK_LISTITEM))
6097 {
6098 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Invalid list item found");
6099 }
6100 if (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Internal))
6101 {
6102 children().append<DocInternal>(parser(),thisVariant());
6103 retval = children().get_last<DocInternal>()->parse(1);
6104 }
6105 } while (!retval.is_any_of(TokenRetval::TK_NONE,TokenRetval::TK_EOF,TokenRetval::RetVal_Section));
6106 if (lastPar) lastPar->markLast();
6107
6108 //printf("DocRoot::parse() retval=%d %d\n",retval,TokenRetval::RetVal_Section);
6109 // then parse any number of level1 sections
6110 while (retval.is(TokenRetval::RetVal_Section))
6111 {
6112 if (!parser()->context.token->sectionId.isEmpty())
6113 {
6114 const SectionInfo *sec=SectionManager::instance().find(parser()->context.token->sectionId);
6115 if (sec)
6116 {
6117 children().append<DocSection>(parser(),thisVariant(),
6118 1,
6119 parser()->context.token->sectionId);
6120 retval = children().get_last<DocSection>()->parse();
6121 }
6122 else
6123 {
6124 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Invalid section id '%s'; ignoring section",qPrint(parser()->context.token->sectionId));
6125 retval = Token::make_TK_NONE();
6126 }
6127 }
6128 else
6129 {
6130 warn_doc_error(parser()->context.fileName,parser()->tokenizer.getLineNr(),"Missing id for section; ignoring section");
6131 retval = Token::make_TK_NONE();
6132 }
6133 }
6134
6135 parser()->handleUnclosedStyleCommands();
6136}
